# Wanix WASI fixtures (Go)

Applies when editing Wanix WASI fixture sources, [`build.sh`](../../ops/fixtures/wanix/build.sh), or `tasks/groups/wanix.ts` wasm build tasks. See [`ops/fixtures/wanix/README.md`](../../ops/fixtures/wanix/README.md), skill `wanix-zed-cafe-export`.

## Policy

| Topic | Rule |
|-------|------|
| WASI drop fixtures | **Go only** — `ops/fixtures/wanix/<name>/main.go` |
| Module | Single root [`go.mod`](../../ops/fixtures/wanix/go.mod) at `ops/fixtures/wanix/` |
| Build | [`build.sh`](../../ops/fixtures/wanix/build.sh) — targets `wasi`, `zed-cafe`, `gojs`, `all` |
| Prereq | Go + `git submodule update --init submodules/wanix` |
| Toolchain | **Go** (`GOOS=wasip1 GOARCH=wasm` for WASI; `GOOS=js GOARCH=wasm` for zed-cafe/gojs) |

## Fixtures

| Package | Output | Role |
|---------|--------|------|
| `hello/` | `hello.wasm` | one-shot stdout |
| `hold/` | `hold.wasm` | infinite loop (term-write while running) |
| `termbridge/` | `termbridge.wasm` | term bridge banner + hold |
| `zedcaferead/` | `zedcaferead.wasm` | read `./zed-cafe/stats.json` |
| `zedcafewrite/` | `zedcafewrite.wasm` | overwrite `stats.json` with `guestTouch` |
| `zedcafewritebad/` | `zedcafewritebad.wasm` | schema guard negative (`evil.json`) |
| `zedcafelist/` | `zedcafelist.wasm` | walk `./zed-cafe/` tree |
| `zed-cafe/` | `zed-cafe.wasm` (+ copy to `cafe/public/wanix/`) | gojs export daemon |
| upstream `test/gojs` | `gojscheck.wasm` | terminal smoke test (separate upstream module) |

## Build tasks

| Task | `build.sh` target |
|------|-------------------|
| `wanix:wasm:build` | `wasi` |
| `wanix:zed-cafe:build` | `zed-cafe` |
| `wanix:gojs:build` | `gojs` |
| `wanix:wasm:build:all` | `all` (wasi + zed-cafe) |

## Prohibited

- New `.c` or `.wat` Wanix drop fixtures
- `wasi-sdk`, `wabt`, `build-wasm-c.sh`, `build-wasm.sh`, `install-wasi-sdk.sh`
- `wanix:wasm:build:c` task id (removed — use `wanix:wasm:build`)
- Separate `go.mod` per fixture subdirectory
- Nesting WASI packages under `wasi/` (flat layout under `ops/fixtures/wanix/`)

## Allowed

- Go `wasip1` packages under `ops/fixtures/wanix/<name>/`
- Go `js/wasm` export daemon under `ops/fixtures/wanix/zed-cafe/`

Cross-link: rule `fixtures.mdc`, rule `wanix-term-bridge.mdc`.
